<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-1357] SpanScorer does not respect ConstantScoreRangeQuery setting</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-1357</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;ConstantScoreRangeQuery is actually on and can&apos;t be disabled when it should default to off with the option to turn it on.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
            <key id="12402414">LUCENE-1357</key>
            <summary>SpanScorer does not respect ConstantScoreRangeQuery setting</summary>
